✨ Cinema shapes how we see the world — and sometimes, how we see women.
Behind the glitz and glamour lies a troubling legacy: stories where women are sidelined, sensationalised, or silenced.
It’s time we asked harder questions. It’s time we imagined better narratives.
Because what we consume, consumes us too.
